# Local DEBUG config for `npm run dev` only (read server-side by dev-broker.ts).
# Copy to .env. .env is gitignored — never commit secrets. Everything is OPTIONAL.
#
# OWOX (data-mart) data is read from your HOST's configured project automatically —
# the dev broker reuses the owox_key from ../owox-data-marts-experimental/secrets,
# exactly like the real host. No OWOX API key goes here. If the host isn't configured,
# the harness falls back to canned sample marts.

# Only if your host checkout lives somewhere other than the sibling directory:
# OWOX_HOST_DIR=../owox-data-marts-experimental

# GitHub (optional grant): set BOTH for real pushes; omit and pushes are just logged.
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...
# GITHUB_REPO=owner/repo
# GITHUB_BRANCH=main

# AI provider (optional grant): stubbed in dev by default — wire a provider in
# dev-broker.ts if you want to test the real catalog overview.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
